			<div id="post-1817" class="post-1817 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-depression tag-economic-collapse tag-false-recovery tag-inflation tag-monitary-pollicy">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/what-will-a-us-economic-collapse-look-like" title="Permalink to Episode-428- What Will a U.S. Economic Collapse Look Like" rel="bookmark">Episode-428- What Will a U.S. Economic Collapse Look Like</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/what-will-a-us-economic-collapse-look-like" title="11:25 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">April 30, 2010</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/what-will-a-us-economic-collapse-look-like#comments" title="Comment on Episode-428- What Will a U.S. Economic Collapse Look Like">11 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton1817" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fwhat-will-a-us-economic-collapse-look-like&amp;text=Episode-428-%20What%20Will%20a%20U.S.%20Economic%20Collapse%20Look%20Like&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fwhat-will-a-us-economic-collapse-look-like" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
