			<div id="post-1787" class="post-1787 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-aquifer-depleation tag-articulture tag-food-prices tag-food-supply tag-gmo">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/damage-done-by-agriculture" title="Permalink to Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture" rel="bookmark">Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/damage-done-by-agriculture" title="11:53 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">April 22, 2010</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/damage-done-by-agriculture#comments" title="Comment on Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture">3 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton1787" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fdamage-done-by-agriculture&amp;text=Episode-422-%20The%20Damage%20Done%20By%20Agriculture&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fdamage-done-by-agriculture" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
<div class="podpress_playerspace podpress_playerspace_audio_mp3 podpress_mp3player" style="display:block;" ><div id="podPressPlayerSpace_7"><!-- podPress --></div></div>
<div class="podPress_downloadlinks podPress_downloadlinks_audio_mp3"><a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/4-10/epi-00422-the-destruction-of-modern-agriculture.mp3" target="new" title="Download: Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture" class="podpress_downloadimglink podpress_downloadimglink_audio_mp3"><img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/audio_mp3_button.png" class="podPress_imgicon podpress_imgicon_audio_mp3" alt="" /></a> <span class="podpress_mediafile_title podpress_mediafile_title_audio_mp3">Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture</span> <span class="podpress_mediafile_dursize podpress_mediafile_dursize_audio_mp3">[ 1:05:16 ]</span> <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_7" class="podpress_playlink podpress_playlink_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressShowHidePlayer('7', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/4-10/epi-00422-the-destruction-of-modern-agriculture.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress//images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;"><span id="podPressPlayerSpace_7_PlayLink" class="podPress_playerspace_playlink">Play Now</span></a><input type="hidden" id="podPressPlayerSpace_7_OrigURL" value="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/4-10/epi-00422-the-destruction-of-modern-agriculture.mp3" /> | <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_7" class="podpress_playinpopup podpress_playinpopup_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressPopupPlayer('7', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/4-10/epi-00422-the-destruction-of-modern-agriculture.mp3', 290, 24, 'The Survival Podcast', '1787', 'Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;">Play in Popup</a> | <a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/4-10/epi-00422-the-destruction-of-modern-agriculture.mp3" target="new" class="podpress_downloadlink podpress_downloadlink_audio_mp3">Download</a></div></div>
<script type="text/javascript">podPressShowHidePlayer('7', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/4-10/epi-00422-the-destruction-of-modern-agriculture.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress//images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-422- The Damage Done By Agriculture', 'The Survival Podcast');</script><p>We rely on our modern agriculture system to feed the planet.  While most people in the modern world seem to believe food comes from a store it most certainly does not.  The bright lights and shiny packaging at the grocery is simply the last step in a long chain of systems.</p>
<p>The reality is be it animal or vegetable it all starts in the farm fields of the world and those fields are sick and dying for a variety of reasons.  Of course man&#8217;s solution is genetic engineering, new chemicals and attempting to adapt to the damage we are doing vs. reversing it.</p>
<p><span style="color: #800000;"><strong>Join me today as we discuss the following recent news stories about this problem&#8230;</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Peak Phosphorus &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2010/04/20/peak_phosphorus" target="_blank">what is it, why should you care</a></li>
<li>Time and Water &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="http://www.aolnews.com/earth-day/article/time-water-running-out-for-ogallala-americas-biggest-aquifer/19446923?icid=main|htmlws-main-n|dl1|link2|http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aolnews.com%2Fearth-day%2Farticle%2Ftime-water-running-out-for-ogallala-americas-biggest-aquifer%2F19446923" target="_blank">running out for America&#8217;s largest aquifer</a></li>
<li>Liberty for Pakistan &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="http://www.tradingmarkets.com/news/stock-alert/mon_monsanto-co-and-pakistan-government-sign-mou-for-bt-cotton-912899.html" target="_blank">liberty for Monsanto&#8217;s GMO Cotton</a></li>
<li>Australia&#8217;s Salty Wheat &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="http://www.foodweek.com.au/main-features-page.aspx?ID=7093">why fix a problem you can &#8220;get around&#8221;</a></li>
<li>The Price of Food &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="http://finance.yahoo.com/news/Wholesale-prices-rise-in-apf-299827519.html?x=0&amp;.v=4" target="_blank">the biggest jump in 26 years</a></li>
<li>Ten Years of Scientific Study &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="http://www.theguardian.pe.ca/index.cfm?sid=337320&amp;sc=98" target="_blank">to tell us something we already knew</a></li>
</ul>
