				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-420-what-will-the-false-recovery-look-like" title="12:40 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">April 20, 2010</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-420-what-will-the-false-recovery-look-like#comments" title="Comment on Episode-420- What Will the False Recovery Look Like">20 Comments</a></span>
